      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET MILLIE (8) was well fancied as favourite latest and led for much of the way but faded to place, beaten 2.5 lengths (24.45) at Bendigo in a Grade 5 over 425m. Expected to feature in the finish again. DEMON KYSAIAH (1) led throughout when winning by a space two back hit the frame last time when second and beaten a neck at Healesville (19.83). Will give a great sight again. ORIENTAL EMERALD (2) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing second (23.17) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. Form from her last run is proving strong. Hard to beat again. GOT A MESSAGE (7) was in the money last start and likely to feature again.",
